---
title: Caramelised Beef Rump & Onion Subs with Fries, Avocado & Herby Mayo
description: When you’re short on time but craving something you can devour with all your favourite components, a beef sub is the only option. Make it your own by customising it with caramelised onions, avocado and a creamy herb mayo. Add a side of fries and you’ll be humming in bliss!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/675bba48c16ec378c8405a6e-db6c4722.jpeg
